title: Bridger Canyon - 1-in-40 development potential
name: Bridger Canyon - 1-in-40 development potential
description:
Additional development potential in Bridger Canyon at the underlying density of one dwelling per 40 acres.

Assumes that 
- public lands remain undeveloped. 
- density is 1-in-40 (subject to 10% roundoff rule)
- existing conservation easements and other restrictions are ignored
